{"title":"市场怪现象","authors":["池北偶　江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"市场怪现象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿裤就得穿筒裤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说省工又省布。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论小伙或老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管孙女或祖母。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做的人方便，买的人叫苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高跟皮鞋最时髦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种款式真不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若想买双平底的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍全城也难找。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘叹气，小妹妹跺脚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新鲜水果已运来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆在店里就不卖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到烂了再处理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降价赔钱是活该。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"售货员有理，顾客们无奈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日买菜难又难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天瓜菜堆成山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔬菜多时地上烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔬菜缺时摆空摊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菜场多变幻，市民干瞪眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜奶供应少又少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦乳精多卖不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此等怪事并不怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只缘利润有大小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急煞了妈妈，哭坏了宝宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载《市场》报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}